tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vital_signs_data (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    heart_rate INT,
    blood_pressure VARCHAR,
    temperature FLOAT,
    oxygen_saturation FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE vital_signs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  heart_rate INT,
  blood_pressure VARCHAR(10),
  temperature FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE telemetry_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  telemetry_type VARCHAR(50),
  telemetry_value VARCHAR(255),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE vital_signs (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    heart_rate INT,
    blood_pressure VARCHAR(10),
    temperature FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE telemetry_data (
    telemetry_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    telemetry_data JSON,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE intervention_log (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    intervention_type VARCHAR(50),
    intervention_description TEXT,
    intervention_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE vital_signs (
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    heart_rate INT NOT NULL,
    blood_pressure_sys INT NOT NULL,
    blood_pressure_dia INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE telemetry_data (
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    temperature FLOAT NOT NULL,
    oxygen_saturation INT NOT NULL,
    respiratory_rate INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE patient_info (
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    gender VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    contact_info VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE alerts (
    alert_id INT NOT NULL,
    alert_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    description TEXT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE intervention_records (
    intervention_id INT NOT NULL,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    intervention_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    medication_given VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);
